# Zero GC
* Use primitive type whenever possible
* Use mutable object whenever possible
* Use object pool when object creation is inevitable
* LSB+MSB <=> UUID
* Avoid for-each on object collection
* Avoid stream API
* Avoid autoboxing
* Avoid 

# Threading & Lock-free
* CPU pinning
* Optimistic concurrency control
* CAS
* Volatile
* Circular buffer

